body_html: @mrastegari thanks a lot for sharing this information with us. I think this is going to be really helpful. Do you have any numerical information of how slow this Torch version is compared to the original version using Darknet? @AaronYKing I'm always glad if there are cases where I'm positively surprised about code being shared publicly.
